fields.name: Trek Domane AL 2
fields.description: The Trek Domane AL 2 is an endurance road bike that's perfect for riders who want to go the distance in comfort. With a lightweight aluminum frame, carbon fork, and endurance geometry, this bike is built for long rides on varied terrain.
fields.bicycle_features: Aluminum frame, carbon fork, endurance geometry

fields.name: Specialized Allez Elite
fields.description: The Allez Elite is a premium aluminum road bike that delivers race-ready performance at an accessible price. With its responsive handling and efficient power transfer, it's perfect for competitive riders and enthusiasts alike.
fields.bicycle_features: Premium aluminum frame, carbon fork, race geometry

fields.name: Giant Contend 3
fields.description: The Giant Contend 3 offers exceptional value for riders looking to get into road cycling. With its comfortable geometry and reliable components, it's perfect for fitness rides, commuting, and weekend adventures.
fields.bicycle_features: Aluminum frame, comfortable geometry, reliable components

fields.name: Trek Marlin 7
fields.description: The Trek Marlin 7 is a cross-country mountain bike that's ready to take you places. With its lightweight aluminum frame and capable components, it's perfect for trail adventures and off-road exploration.
fields.bicycle_features: Alpha Gold aluminum frame, RockShox fork, tubeless ready

fields.name: Specialized Rockhopper Sport 29
fields.description: The Rockhopper Sport 29 is built to handle anything the trail throws at you. With its durable construction and reliable components, it's the perfect bike for riders who want to explore beyond the pavement.
fields.bicycle_features: A1 Premium aluminum frame, SR Suntour XCE fork

fields.name: Giant Talon 2
fields.description: The Giant Talon 2 is an aggressive hardtail that's built for the trail. With its lightweight ALUXX aluminum frame and capable suspension fork, it's ready for cross-country adventures.
fields.bicycle_features: ALUXX aluminum frame, SR Suntour XCM fork

fields.name: Trek FX 3 Disc
fields.description: The Trek FX 3 Disc is a versatile hybrid bike that's perfect for fitness rides, commuting, and recreational cycling. With its lightweight frame and disc brakes, it offers comfort and performance.
fields.bicycle_features: Alpha Gold aluminum frame, disc brakes, fitness geometry

fields.name: Specialized Sirrus 3.0
fields.description: The Sirrus 3.0 is designed for riders who want a fast, fun, and efficient ride. With its lightweight frame and fitness-oriented geometry, it's perfect for getting fit and having fun.
fields.bicycle_features: A1 Premium aluminum frame, fitness geometry

fields.name: Trek Verve+ 2
fields.description: The Trek Verve+ 2 is an electric hybrid bike that makes every ride more enjoyable. With its Bosch motor and comfortable design, it's perfect for commuting and recreational rides.
fields.bicycle_features: Bosch Active Line motor, 400Wh battery, comfort geometry

fields.name: Specialized Turbo Vado 3.0
fields.description: The Turbo Vado 3.0 is an electric bike that's built for urban adventures. With its powerful motor and sleek design, it's perfect for commuting and city exploration.
fields.bicycle_features: Specialized SL 1.1 motor, 460Wh battery, urban geometry

fields.name: Giro Register MIPS Helmet
fields.description: The Giro Register MIPS helmet offers essential protection with MIPS technology for enhanced safety. Lightweight and comfortable, it's perfect for recreational cycling.

fields.name: Bell Zephyr MIPS Helmet
fields.description: The Bell Zephyr MIPS helmet combines advanced safety technology with aerodynamic design. Perfect for road cycling and racing applications.

fields.name: Cycling Jersey - Pro Team
fields.description: Professional cycling jersey made from moisture-wicking fabric. Features full-zip front, three rear pockets, and reflective details for visibility.
fields.bicycle_features: Moisture-wicking fabric, full-zip, three rear pockets

fields.name: Cycling Shorts - Padded
fields.description: High-quality cycling shorts with professional-grade chamois padding. Made from compression fabric for comfort during long rides.
fields.bicycle_features: Professional chamois, compression fabric, flatlock seams

fields.name: Cycling Gloves - Full Finger
fields.description: Comfortable cycling gloves with full finger coverage and gel padding. Perfect for long rides and mountain biking.
fields.bicycle_features: Gel padding, breathable fabric, full finger coverage
